adamcom (1.2-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Release 1.2
  * BREAKING: Text mode no longer parses inline flags - use /rpt MS text
  * Added /rpt MS text command for text mode repeat
  * Strict input validation in hex mode (only 0-9, A-F allowed)
  * Malformed flags (e.g., ----r) now rejected with clear error
  * Hex mode inline flags: -id <CAN_ID>, -r (repeat), -t <interval_ms>
  * /rs stop to stop inline repeat, /ra stops all repeats
  * Fixed byte counter: text mode counts all chars, hex mode excludes flags
  * First message sent immediately when starting repeat
  * Added Alt+1-9,0 keyboard shortcuts for presets 1-10
  * Improved preset editor with Edit/Delete options
  * Use - to clear individual fields during edit
  * Updated manual with text/hex mode differences

 -- user <user@Cardinal>  Mon, 29 Dec 2025 18:00:00 +0300

adamcom (1.1-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Major release 1.1
  * Added multi-preset repeat mode (/p N -r -t MS)
  * Added simultaneous preset repeating with independent intervals
  * Added /rs (repeat status) and /ra (stop all) commands
  * Added non-interrupting RX/TX output (typing stays static)
  * Added comprehensive manual (H in Ctrl-T menu)
  * Added command hints to settings menu
  * Added /hex, /can, /clear, /device, /baud, /mode, /crlf, /status commands
  * Updated install.sh with better UX and fallback to source build
  * Improved README.md documentation

 -- user <user@Cardinal>  Sun, 29 Dec 2025 12:00:00 +0300

